#!/usr/bin/env -S /Users/semini/.mlx-env/bin/python
"""thmes — THMES: Thai Hermes Agentic Shell. Local-model TUI with tool calling.

Features:
  • Multimodal chat (text + image + audio)
  • Tool calling loop (read/write/bash/grep/web_fetch/python)
  • 14 built-in agents (loaded from ~/.claude/agents/)
  • 29 built-in skills (loaded from ~/.claude/skills/)
  • Persistent input history + auto-complete

Slash commands:
  /image PATH | /audio PATH       attach for next message
  /agent [NAME|list]              switch persona (analyst, debugger, …)
  /skill [NAME|list]              invoke a skill workflow
  /tool [list|on|off|allow NAME]  manage tool execution
  /auto [on|off|last]             🧠 smart context router
  /context                        📏 show token usage
  /compact [N|on|off|threshold N] 🗜  summarize old turns (auto when >60%)
  /model [NAME|list]              switch model (gemma|qwen-vl|qwen3)
  /system TEXT                    custom system prompt (overrides agent)
  /max N                          set max output tokens (default 2048)
  /clear | /save F | /load F | /stats | /help | /quit

Env vars:
  THMES_MODEL=gemma|qwen-vl|qwen3
  THMES_MAX_TOKENS=2048
  THMES_COMPACT_PCT=0.6
"""
